Definition: of cotton thread that has been treated with sodium hydroxide to shrink it and increase its luster and affinity for dye
Example: mercerized cotton
Synonyms: verb, change, mercerize, mercerised, of, cotton, thread, that, has, been, treated, with, sodium, hydroxide, to, shrink, it, and, increase, its, luster, affinity, for, dye
Category: adj.ppl
